On 11 Jul 2018, at 8:55 am, Matthew Palfrey <matthewpalfrey@gmail.com> wrote:


Hi Heath,

How are things? What's new at WolfIQ?

We have some additional edits for the SBB site if you have some time in the next couple of days?

1. Update the dashboard page here http://www.strongbybret.com/dashboard.php with the following content:

Week 1: July 9 - July 15

Please remember that your first week should be a deload/easier week. There are no set specifications/percentages for this; just be sure you aren't seeking PRs or going to failure during this first week. Now is the time to focus on good form and familiarizing yourself with the workouts.

Week 2: July 16 - July 22

Welcome to Week 2! After a nice deload week you should be ready to increase your effort a bit. Continue to focus on good form and keep a little effort in reserve this week.

Week 3: July 23 - July 29

Welcome to Week 3! It's time to start ramping up the intensity of your workouts while continuing to be mindful of your form. It is recommended that you film and review your exercises at least occasionally to ensure that you are performing the lifts properly.

Week 4: July 30 - August 5

Welcome to Week 4! This is the last week of this month's workout cycle. Now is the time to increase your effort to near-max levels and try for some PRs (personal strength records). Continue to use good form.

2. http://www.strongbybret.com/workouts.php

Change the grid here to read (left to right):

Workout 1 June/July 2018 - links through to a page using this content http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=workouts&action=edit&num=117
Workout 2 June/July 2018 - links through to a page using this content http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=workouts&action=edit&num=118
Workout 3 June/July 2018 - links through to a page using this content http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=workouts&action=edit&num=119

3. Update the main navigation 'Your Program' link list to reflect the 3 current workout pages.

4. We need the following exercises added into the exercise list here: http://www.strongbybret.com/library.php

Please add them in alphabetical order.

Assisted Pistol Squat - using content from http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=exercises&action=edit&num=257

Close-Grip Incline Press - using content from http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=exercises&action=edit&num=255

Deficit Db Reverse Lunge - using content from http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=exercises&action=edit&num=256

Knee-Banded Bodyweight Glute Bridge/Abduction Countdown - using content from http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=exercises&action=edit&num=258

YTWL - using content from http://bretcontreras.com/cms/admin.php?menu=exercises&action=edit&num=259
